data.description: Welcome to 1709 Tuscany Lane, nestled in the Holt school district. This charming residence boasts three bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a generously sized fenced backyard providing a haven of privacy. The recently updated kitchen adds a touch of modern elegance with plenty of countertop and cabinet space for all your cooking needs. Enjoy the convenience of an attached 2-car garage with ample storage. This home is exceptionally low maintenance, featuring newer appliances and furnace. The roof was replaced in 2012, and the property showcases a sprawling fenced backyard for your enjoyment. All appliances, including the basement freezer, are included. Take advantage of the rare combination of comfort and practicality in this lovely abode.
